> Coupling vs cohesion.
>
> Coupling:
>
> - Can be hard to find
> - Can be really hard &/| expensive to eliminate.
>
> Cohesive sub-elements are:
>
> - Usually easy to find
> - Cheap to achieve, &
> - Help you find de-coupling.

